    "Follow signs to 'Trains' — platforms below Arrivals Hall",
    "Train to Amsterdam Centraal: 15-20 min, \u20ac5-6 — buy OV-chipkaart (reusable)",
    "Buy ticket at yellow NS machines — Intercity Direct is fastest",
